data.title: Do you know anyone who has been to Russia's Siberia?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 35): Funny you would ask. I actually know a guy. We worked together at well known Ukrainian aircraft design company. He had prestigious job, great group of young people he enjoyed working with, bright future to look forward to, but then, one day he decided to go live in Siberia.
